(522, 5, 'prebanner_sublist_0_content', '<p>Greyrock systems can accept a variety of input feedstocks. Abundant natural gas and natural gas liquids (ethane, propane, etc.) are ideal in oversupplied natural gasmarkets. In addiFon, waste gases from industrial processes and even waste biomass.</p>'),
